name: Carnival Delight
description:
This is a iconic figure of the carnival from Oliveira -MG Brazil. 
They called it cainágua. This figure has it's origin based on sacred and festivity elements. A mix between figures from catholic processions and figures from carnival of Rio de Janeiro. Nobody normally knows who is inside that costume,and that is what makes this figure so curious, atracting people to play with anonymity.
